  "faqs": [
    {
      "question": "What is the Bharti Hexacom IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Bharti Hexacom IPO<!-- --> is a <b>main-board<!-- --> <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> of <!-- -->75000000<!-- --> equity shares</b> of the face value of ₹<!-- -->5<!-- --> aggregating up to ₹<!-- -->4,275.00<!-- --> Crores. The issue is priced at <span>₹570 per share</span>. The minimum order quantity is <!-- -->26<!-- -->.</p><p>The <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> <b>opens on <!-- -->April 3, 2024</b>, and <b>closes on <!-- -->April 5, 2024</b>.</p><p>Kfin Technologies Limited<!-- --> is the registrar for the <!-- -->IPO<!-- -->. The shares are proposed to be listed on <!-- -->BSE, NSE<!-- -->.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply in Bharti Hexacom IPO through Zerodha?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Zerodha customers can apply online in <!-- -->Bharti Hexacom IPO<!-- --> using UPI as a payment gateway. Zerodha customers can apply in <!-- -->Bharti Hexacom IPO<!-- --> by login into Zerodha Console (back office) and submitting an IPO application form.</p><p><strong>Steps to apply in <!-- -->Bharti Hexacom IPO<!-- --> through Zerodha</strong></p><ol><li>Visit the Zerodha website and login to Console.</li><li>Go to Portfolio and click the IPOs link.</li><li>Go to the '<!-- -->Bharti Hexacom IPO<!-- -->' row and click the 'Bid' button.</li><li>Enter your UPI ID, Quantity, and Price.</li><li>Submit IPO application form.</li><li>Visit the UPI App (net banking or BHIM) to approve the mandate.</li></ol><p>Visit <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Application Process Review\">Zerodha IPO Application Process Review</a> for more detail.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When Bharti Hexacom IPO will open?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The Bharti Hexacom IPO opens on April 3, 2024 and closes on April 5, 2024.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the lot size of Bharti Hexacom IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Bharti Hexacom IPO<!-- --> <b>lot size is <!-- -->26</b>, and the <b>minimum amount required is <span>₹14,820</span></b>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply for Bharti Hexacom IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>You can apply in <!-- -->Bharti Hexacom IPO<!-- --> online using either <a href=\"/article/upi-payment-option-ipo-application-explained/382/\">UPI</a> or ASBA as a payment method. ASBA IPO application is available in the net banking of your bank account. UPI IPO application is offered by brokers who don't offer banking services. Read more detail about applying IPO online through <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Review\"><b>Zerodha</b></a>, <a href=\"/broker/upstox/ipo/33/\" title=\"Upstox IPO Review\">Upstox</a>, <a href=\"/broker/5paisa/ipo/4/\" title=\"5Paisa IPO Review\">5Paisa</a>, <a href=\"/broker/edelweiss_broking/ipo/34/\" title=\"Nuvama IPO Review\">Nuvama</a>, <a href=\"/broker/hdfc-securities/ipo/6/\" title=\"HDFC Bank IPO Review\">HDFC Bank</a>, and <a href=\"/broker/sbi-capital/ipo/19/\" title=\"SBI Capital IPO Review\">SBI Bank</a>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When is Bharti Hexacom IPO allotment?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The finalization of Basis of Allotment for <!-- -->Bharti Hexacom IPO<!-- --> will be done on <!-- -->Monday, April 8, 2024<!-- -->, and the allotted shares will be credited to your demat account by <!-- -->Wednesday, April 10, 2024<!-- -->. Check the <a href=\"/ipo_allotment_status/bharti-hexacom-ipo/1694/\" title=\"Bharti Hexacom IPO Allotment Status\">Bharti Hexacom IPO<!-- --> allotment status</a>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When is Bharti Hexacom IPO listing date?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The <!-- -->Bharti Hexacom IPO<!-- --> listing date is on <b>Friday, April 12, 2024</b>.</p></div>"
